content: --अंत {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {1} [न. ब.] not alone so as to exclude all others, uncertain, doubtful, variable; स्यादित्यव्ययमनेकांतवाचकं {2} = अनैकांतिक <ab>q. v.</ab> (--तः {1} unsettled condition, absence of permanence. {2} uncertainty, doubtfulness. {3} an unessential part, as the several {%anubandhas%}.
